title: Games & TV lounge, Catering kitchen, Raised garden beds
posting_body: ['Live where ideas and interests ignite', 'Be among the first to live in The Spring District in Bellevue, Washington.', 'We are creating a neighborhood that draws people in, sparks both business and personal passions weaving an intellectual tapestry that drives new ideas.', 'Sparc Apartments is the catalyst welcoming you to a new living experience where urban meets suburban.', 'Lease studios, one, two and three bedroom apartments.', 'Not to mention innovative Townhomes and Live work lofts.', 'Live minutes from Downtown Bellevue, Kirkland, Redmond with easy access to I-405 and the Microsoft Campus.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 166', 'OR Text', '166', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text us.', 'See our property details here:', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 731 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Floor-to-ceiling windows in select homes', '- Full size, stacked washer and dryer', '- Electric or gas range', '- Patios and balconies in select homes', '- Berber carpet and vinyl plank flooring', '- Custom pendant lights in kitchen', '- Stainless or black Whirlpool appliances', '- Quartz countertops in kitchen and bathrooms', 'Community Amenities', '- Raised garden beds', '- Early childhood education center', '- Catering kitchen', '- Well-stocked fitness center', '- Bicycle storage & repair station', '- Wi-Fi Lounge', '- Games & TV lounge', '- Mini putting green', '- Public courtyard', '- Pet washing station', '- Rooftop deck', '- 4,500 SF outdoor playground', '- Greenhouse', '- Event space', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday-Sunday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Sparc at Spring District', '1201 121st Avenue NE, Bellevue, WA, 98005', 'i74VBs5exV']
